{"tid":715821,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[改下歌詞] 矛盾英軍 － 英格蘭對巴拿馬","createTime":"2018-06-24T19:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T21:34:51.000Z","uid":55650,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b14dcd56272f213a550ae00ba0525a74019baefb","tid":715821,"uid":55650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:10:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PPCIWIbrLz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPPCIWIbrLz4&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e217cd85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PPCIWIbrLz4</a><br />\n<br />\n見到有人火速剪咗今場英格蘭對巴拿馬，陳詠謙又改撚咗歌詞<br />\n又畀佢講中入過5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n矛盾英軍（原曲：矛盾一生）<br />\n改編詞：陳詠謙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花巧一刻開心 過後不開心<br />\n的波都不開心 誰責任<br />\n死推死扭最後還是不發奮<br />\n永遠看不見入球 大賽腳震<br />\n<br />\n矛盾只因亂咁做 踢得差<br />\n誰期望這刻英格蘭 唔大炒㗎<br />\n你為我插一輪膠花 你哋唔好啦<br />\n控定起腳入球算吧<br />\n抬頭見對手比較弱 進攻啦<br />\n起碼入五粒回家<br />\n當你遲遲未起腳 就讓我起腳吧<br />\n我替你入波好嗎"},{"pid":"914ae986fe4759f808bb2be3d0ab04b6a9b8aadd","tid":715821,"uid":372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:28:18.000Z","msg":"啲詞完全冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d0c511e077f21a1a6d51a7c06627a85ab87892","tid":715821,"uid":143768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"914ae986fe4759f808bb2be3d0ab04b6a9b8aadd","tid":715821,"uid":372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:28:18.000Z","msg":"啲詞完全冇意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T19:30:09.000Z","msg":"只係每句換一兩個詞語咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a266fd85c724bf9b0e172e0fbe3ef2a40f149d","tid":715821,"uid":62633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/PPCIWIbrLz4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPPCIWIbrLz4&d=qZBLZG8yiywiUcYiUXUpe8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=e217cd85\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PPCIWIbrLz4</a><br />\n<br />\n見到有人<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>火速</strong></span>剪咗今場英格蘭對巴拿馬，陳詠謙又改撚咗歌詞<br />\n又畀佢講中入過5粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n花巧一刻開心 過後不開心<br />\n的波都不開心 誰責任<br />\n死推死扭最後還是不發奮<br />\n永遠看不見入球 大賽腳震<br />\n<br />\n<strong>矛盾只因亂咁做 踢得差</strong><br />\n誰期望這刻英格蘭 唔大炒㗎<br />\n你為我插一輪膠花 你哋唔好啦<br />\n控定起腳入球算吧<br />\n抬頭見對手比較弱 進攻啦<br />\n起碼入五粒回家<br />\n當你遲遲未起腳 就讓我起腳吧<br />\n我替你入波好嗎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨見到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">火速</span></strong></span>呢兩個字都諗緊係咪求其每句換一兩個詞語咁就算<br />\n<br />\n如果我估波都有咁準就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首歌而家就真係<strong>矛盾只因亂咁作 改得差</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有心改不如慢慢組織下場波兩隊表現再諗過, 慢工出細貨"},{"pid":"94de661812a1c66a3f734c8db7f468ce050a28b8","tid":715821,"uid":147159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T20:39:55.000Z","msg":"算啦收撚皮啦你估你邊撚個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca86af34551f968f814f8104020d81ec2b1285e3","tid":715821,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T21:28:44.000Z","msg":"同有線歌神冇得比"},{"pid":"a156d63185431c377436f4864c4d9a166c3e8fe5","tid":715821,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T21:34:51.000Z","msg":"哈利簡尼哈哈哈<br />\n場場搏命未話謝"}]}